<body>
    <h1>隐私政策 / Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>中文（简体）</h2>
<p><strong>PulseOSC 尊重并保护您的隐私。</strong></p>
<p><strong>健康数据的使用：</strong> 本应用需要访问您的健康数据（仅限实时心率），该数据仅会通过 OSC 协议发送至<strong>您在设置中指定的 IP 地址或域名</strong>。我们绝不会收集、存储、上传或与任何无关第三方分享您的健康数据。</p>
<p><strong>数据传输与控制：</strong> 数据传输的目标完全由您控制。应用仅会连接到您配置的目标地址（可能是本地设备，也可能是您指定的远程服务器）。除此之外，应用不会连接任何其他外部服务器，也不会将数据发送给开发者。</p>
<p>如有任何问题，欢迎随时联系我们。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>English</h2>
<p><strong>PulseOSC respects and protects your privacy.</strong></p>
<p><strong>HealthKit Usage:</strong> This app accesses your health data (specifically real-time heart rate) solely to transmit it via OSC protocol to the <strong>IP address or domain you specify in the settings</strong>. We do not collect, store, upload, or share your health data with any unrelated third parties.</p>
<p><strong>Data Transmission & Control:</strong> You have full control over where your data is sent. The app only connects to the target address you configure (which may be a local device or a remote server of your choice). Aside from this, the app does not connect to any external servers and sends no data to the developer.</p>
<p>If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us.</p>
    </div>
